original_title: CHIKARA Through Savage Progress Cuts the Jungle Line
overview: Japanese legend Manami Toyota makes the second appearance of her U.S. debut weekend teaming with Mike Quackenbush against the BDK's Claudio Castagnoli and Manami Toyota, UltraMantis Black looks to recruit Hallowicked for his Torneo Cibernetico team, Frightmare defends the CHIKARA Young Lions Cup against the BDK's Pinkie Sanchez, and more.
title: CHIKARA Through Savage Progress Cuts the Jungle Line
